deploying three satellites and repairing an ailing satellite 
lounge said there hasnt been much tension at home about the 
upcoming mission his wife kathryn anne is an engineer at the 
johnson space center and she understands the challenges as well 
as i do his family including his children shannon 17 kenneth 
7 and kathy 4 plan to be there for the liftoff 
to my two little children who live at home it hasnt become 
real to them yet we talk about going to florida and how they get 
to go watch daddy launch and they get to go to disney world and im 
not sure which is the more important of the two 
but seriously lounge said his children do understand what he 
does 
a couple of times my 4yearold has talked about how youre 
going to go fly in the space shuttle but its not going to blow up 
right so shes remembering that image of challenger he said 
but its not like a cloud of anxiety thats following her 
around she wanted some reassurance and i reassured her and that 
was ok because daddy knows everything he said smiling 
lounge a member of the texas air national guard who flies with 
his unit at least once a week said he doesnt think much about the 
risks and dangers 
but its characteristic of people that get into this kind of 
profession that were all bulletproof you can shoot at me but 
you cant hit me it might hit someone else but it wont hit me 
he said 
