through 1995 while other european producers will deliver about 
575 much of those will go to countries other than the united 
states but about 128 billion will go to us operators he said 
on balance nebinger said the us still emerges as a very 
strong winner in the importexport balance with exports to europe 
exceeding imports by 132 billion 
the impact on the us trade deficit he said cannot be 
overemphasized 
